WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:00.120 --> 00:00:01.377
Hey, good morning, family.

00:00:01.377 --> 00:00:03.040
How are you all doing today?

00:00:03.400 --> 00:00:05.200
I have my wife with me again.

00:00:08.000 --> 00:00:15.663
The Lord told me, 'Brandon, she's not to walk behind you; she's to walk beside you concerning things.

00:00:15.663 --> 00:00:17.790
' I want her on the broadcast more.

00:00:17.790 --> 00:00:19.735
I want her to come on and talk more.

00:00:22.459 --> 00:00:24.462
She has a lot inside of her.

00:00:25.564 --> 00:00:34.476
She's been in the background doing emails and things like that, and now we're homeschooling the kids and getting ready for this new school year.

00:00:34.867 --> 00:00:39.989
It's a lot, but there is so much inside of her, and I want to hear more.

00:00:40.316 --> 00:00:43.706
I'm going to bring her on more and we're going to talk.

00:00:45.680 --> 00:00:52.160
The Lord told me a couple of days ago—I've had some amazing visitations in the last two weeks.

00:00:52.933 --> 00:01:25.853
The intensity of the river has doubled on my life with the things the Lord is showing me.

00:01:26.048 --> 00:01:32.106
I call it the prophetic pulse.

00:01:37.188 --> 00:01:51.519
I'm so humbled that He would come and visit me, but it's for you all.

00:01:51.519 --> 00:01:53.240
He instructs me about my own life—things that I can't talk about.

00:02:04.942 --> 00:02:31.749
I try to talk about it and people say, 'Well, you're bragging,' so I've realized there are a lot of things I just keep quiet now.

00:02:31.749 --> 00:02:52.391
I'm learning; this whole thing has been like a fire hydrant shot right at me.

00:02:59.879 --> 00:03:08.740
The Lord said, 'Brandon, you can't talk about some of this stuff.

00:03:08.740 --> 00:03:32.589
' I realized some of the things He's showing me are for me to pray over personally.

00:03:32.589 --> 00:03:42.900
I'm a work in progress.

00:03:42.900 --> 00:04:11.067
Diana and I are just grabbing on with both fingers and our teeth, saying we're not letting go.

00:04:11.067 --> 00:04:23.089
People want to know how Megan is doing.

00:04:23.089 --> 00:04:31.680
She's getting better and better.

00:04:31.680 --> 00:04:45.794
A miracle is a miracle even if it's progressive.

00:05:00.084 --> 00:05:25.919
The doctor said she would stay at the mental capability of a two-and-a-half-year-old for the rest of her life, but we're believing God that we're going up.

00:05:25.919 --> 00:05:49.820
She's come a long way, but we still have a long way to go.

00:05:49.820 --> 00:06:30.855
For the first time in years, we are able to go to church as a family and not just watch online because of the distraction she had been in public.

00:06:32.689 --> 00:07:03.240
The ushers used to have us leave because she was so disruptive, but now we can sit in the back and pray for the people.

00:07:09.120 --> 00:07:09.274
It's been such a blessing.

00:07:09.274 --> 00:07:22.790
They're having a prayer conference in Branson, Missouri.

00:07:22.790 --> 00:07:46.124
Sister Billie Brim is going to be having a prayer conference in October.

00:07:46.124 --> 00:08:04.688
I think it would be wonderful if you all support her.

00:08:06.662 --> 00:08:24.906
The Lord showed me a great move of God coming for that area.

00:08:24.906 --> 00:08:55.520
Great signs and wonders are coming to Branson, Missouri, and the Lord told me it's going to start with Billie Brim.

00:08:55.520 --> 00:09:02.940
I asked, 'Why her, Lord?

00:09:02.940 --> 00:09:23.479
' and He said, 'Because she asks for it over and over.

00:09:23.479 --> 00:10:04.480
' I saw a Shekinah Glory cloud, like a thick fog, the presence of the Lord coming in like it did in the Old Testament.

00:10:06.384 --> 00:10:24.373
I saw a glory cloud come in while she's doing prayer.

00:10:41.879 --> 00:10:42.199
I anticipate it every time.

00:10:43.603 --> 00:10:53.991
It will be birthed out of love and prayer.

00:10:53.991 --> 00:11:03.185
They will have a major move of God.

00:11:12.520 --> 00:11:39.640
I saw a glory cloud coming in and people being healed when that presence of the Lord comes into that auditorium.

00:11:39.640 --> 00:11:56.080
Everyone will be healed in that service—nothing missing, nothing broken, Shalom.

00:11:56.080 --> 00:12:12.253
It's time for an outpouring like we've never seen before.

00:12:12.253 --> 00:12:42.519
The Lord said, 'Brandon, you need to talk about the things that I'm going to do and the glorious outpouring.

00:12:42.519 --> 00:13:12.200
' He told me to inspire His people and go back to the basics—to teach prayer and the Word.

00:13:12.200 --> 00:13:16.600
That's the balance.

00:13:21.029 --> 00:14:13.484
You have to have the Word as a balance; it's like a teeter-totter that keeps you from getting off into weirdo land.

00:14:13.484 --> 00:14:40.000
We want to follow the Holy Spirit in our lives and ministry.

00:14:43.152 --> 00:15:10.370
The bottom line is teaching you how to stand by faith and pray in the Spirit.

00:15:10.370 --> 00:15:21.324
If you don't pray in tongues, you're missing out.

00:15:21.324 --> 00:15:29.036
Praying in the Spirit stirs yourself up.

00:15:29.036 --> 00:16:04.653
Diana and I keep going despite the waves that have knocked us down over the years.

00:16:04.653 --> 00:16:41.687
We will serve the Lord, fighting the good fight of faith and standing on the Word as Holy Ghost-filled Christians who will not compromise.

00:16:41.687 --> 00:16:58.051
We will not bend our knee to Baal.

00:17:04.720 --> 00:17:10.589
I met Diana at Jeremy Pearsons' Bible study.

00:17:10.589 --> 00:17:32.867
We've been together since she was 15 and married for over 20 years.

00:17:32.867 --> 00:17:47.659
We've stayed together through everything because of prayer and love.

00:17:47.659 --> 00:18:22.060
I can be a rascal and I'm not always easy to be with, but we're going to make it.

00:18:22.060 --> 00:18:57.488
For those of you who are weary because you aren't seeing your manifestation, I want to inspire you to keep on keeping on.

00:18:57.488 --> 00:19:02.514
Stand therefore.

00:19:02.514 --> 00:19:30.697
What keeps us going is the Word of God and finding books that fan that flame.

00:19:30.697 --> 00:19:53.000
I love the book *The Man Who Talks with the Flowers* about George Washington Carver.

00:19:53.000 --> 00:20:05.200
It's an older book by Glenn Clark.

00:20:05.200 --> 00:20:18.187
Carver's relationship with the Lord inspires me.

00:20:18.187 --> 00:20:43.760
Because I have learning disabilities and don't read well, Diana reads to me.

00:20:43.760 --> 00:20:56.400
She reads at least 50 books a year.

00:21:03.799 --> 00:21:11.480
The simplicity of his relationship with God is beautiful.

00:21:11.480 --> 00:21:33.818
It doesn't have to be complicated; we should come to God like a child.

00:21:33.818 --> 00:21:41.253
What fans your flame?

00:21:41.253 --> 00:22:05.600
For me, it's books like this and the healing testimonies of Azusa Street.

00:22:05.600 --> 00:22:21.565
I've been reading *True Stories of the Miracles of Azusa Street*.

00:22:21.565 --> 00:22:35.570
If He did it once, He'll do it again.

00:22:39.086 --> 00:22:45.440
God is no respecter of persons.

00:22:45.440 --> 00:22:59.385
I've seen a great revival and that glory cloud coming.

00:22:59.385 --> 00:23:20.980
One last call: if you truly realize how much Jesus loves you—He oozes love.

00:23:20.980 --> 00:23:38.155
Being touched by the Father changes you and makes you soft.

00:23:38.155 --> 00:24:18.260
Two nights ago, I was on a ladder putting a new light up, and the presence of the Lord hit me so hard I had to get down.

00:24:20.154 --> 00:24:43.1000
I saw again what's coming: I saw the devil and all the principalities and legions behind him.

00:24:43.1000 --> 00:25:01.697
They were at attention, looking at the Father, knowing their time was up.

00:25:02.851 --> 00:25:13.439
The light from the Father's throne was blinding.

00:25:13.439 --> 00:25:25.629
I saw Satan cowered down, hunkered toward the ground.

00:25:25.629 --> 00:25:38.439
He knew the sun had set on humanity.

00:25:38.439 --> 00:25:43.240
Jesus is coming.

00:25:43.240 --> 00:26:03.275
If your heart is not right, you're going to get left.

00:26:03.275 --> 00:26:18.306
Get your heart right before the Father right now.

00:26:18.306 --> 00:26:35.259
If you're walking on the fence, woe unto you.

00:26:35.259 --> 00:27:05.520
Satan was cowering, melting down like a fool because he turned his back on the King of Kings.

00:27:11.159 --> 00:27:12.845
The principalities and powers looked worried.

00:27:12.845 --> 00:27:28.279
They knew they made the wrong choice by following the devil.

00:27:28.279 --> 00:27:45.780
Every knee will bow and every tongue will confess that Jesus Christ is Lord.

00:27:45.780 --> 00:27:52.947
Even those devils will tremble.

00:28:07.389 --> 00:28:15.589
We are about to step into our glorified bodies and rule with Him forever.

00:28:15.589 --> 00:28:37.350
I saw a major move of God coming to Hollywood—to A-list celebrities like Justin Bieber.

00:28:37.350 --> 00:28:50.320
They are hurting and thirsty for more.

00:28:50.320 --> 00:29:21.301
They will have a great influence in bringing others to the kingdom because God will touch even the hardest people.

00:29:24.199 --> 00:29:45.160
I want to read a beautiful testimony about a healing that took place at Azusa Street.

00:29:45.509 --> 00:30:02.467
The Lord told me He wants His people to believe bigger.

00:30:02.467 --> 00:30:21.560
This story is of a child whose second teeth grew in rotten and black.

00:30:21.560 --> 00:30:31.160
Lucille said, 'God will heal anything.

00:30:31.160 --> 00:30:50.279
' Lucille laid a handkerchief over the child's mouth and prayed.

00:30:55.623 --> 00:31:03.346
A handful of blackened teeth dropped into a cup.

00:31:19.684 --> 00:31:20.035
Then new teeth grew in one at a time.

00:31:31.475 --> 00:31:31.720
The child said it kind of tickled.

00:31:31.720 --> 00:32:02.959
Sister Lucille was a little woman, but she could command a leg to grow or a wrist to heal.

00:32:02.959 --> 00:32:16.359
She described the Shekinah Glory as a mist-like cloud.

00:32:16.359 --> 00:32:36.027
She would sit in it and play in it, and it was like breathing in pure oxygen.

00:32:36.027 --> 00:32:44.705
The scent was like lilacs or roses.

00:32:44.705 --> 00:33:21.979
When they would sing in the Spirit, the glory would rise and fill the whole room.

00:33:21.979 --> 00:33:38.310
Megan is going to be radically healed like that.

00:33:38.320 --> 00:33:45.240
I'm expecting it.

00:33:46.644 --> 00:34:15.725
It will be a sign to the world that Jesus Christ is the same yesterday, today, and forever.

00:34:15.725 --> 00:34:31.319
I'm trying to inspire you to believe bigger.

00:34:32.906 --> 00:34:51.943
This is how I keep myself afloat—testimonies and Kenneth Hagin's books.

00:34:51.943 --> 00:35:01.965
Faith comes by hearing.

00:35:01.965 --> 00:35:15.330
We have challenges, but God is faithful.

00:35:15.330 --> 00:35:31.833
We live by faith, selling on eBay and Poshmark.

00:35:31.833 --> 00:35:55.672
Here is a testimony from a brother who had a visitation from Jesus.

00:36:02.142 --> 00:36:21.743
He was praying at his kitchen table and saw a vision of himself in a field.

00:36:30.735 --> 00:36:43.461
The Lord walked up and said, 'Come on, get up; it's time to work.

00:36:43.461 --> 00:37:03.200
' He wore simple white robes and had dark skin, long hair, and a dark beard.

00:37:03.200 --> 00:37:27.214
They walked through hills of cattle, and the Lord said, 'I need a cowboy.

00:37:27.214 --> 00:37:41.426
' The brother said, 'You've got one, Lord.

00:37:41.426 --> 00:38:12.200
' The Lord said, 'A cowboy needs a horse,' and the brother replied, 'Even a string of horses, Lord.

00:38:12.200 --> 00:38:23.270
' It made Him smile.

00:38:28.799 --> 00:38:33.440
Jesus communicates as a friend.

00:38:33.440 --> 00:38:50.880
If you don't know Him, this is your last call.

00:38:50.880 --> 00:38:58.415
Will you bow your knee today?

00:39:02.266 --> 00:39:11.991
No sin is too big for Jesus to forgive.

00:39:11.991 --> 00:39:26.520
Say this prayer: 'Jesus, I'm a sinner.

00:39:26.520 --> 00:39:41.209
Write my name in the Lamb's Book of Life.

00:39:46.053 --> 00:39:54.160
I believe You are the Son of God.

00:39:54.160 --> 00:40:04.755
Forgive me of my sins.

00:40:04.755 --> 00:40:14.160
I want to come home.

00:40:14.160 --> 00:40:34.860
Thank You for setting me free from sin, sickness, and disease.

00:40:34.860 --> 00:40:53.125
' Now, find a Bible and a good church.

00:40:53.125 --> 00:41:01.674
Let's believe for your miracle now.

00:41:01.674 --> 00:41:42.520
Father, in the name of Jesus, I believe they are healed from the top of their head to the soles of their feet.

00:41:42.520 --> 00:41:49.480
Cancer, go now.

00:41:49.480 --> 00:41:59.100
Diabetes, go now.

00:41:59.100 --> 00:42:13.053
We call for new organs, restored eyesight, and hearing.

00:42:15.343 --> 00:42:24.400
I call for healing from strokes.

00:42:24.400 --> 00:42:35.954
We command tumors to shrivel and go.

00:42:35.954 --> 00:42:55.109
I thank You for restoration in the colon, stomach, and thyroid.

00:42:57.415 --> 00:43:11.880
I call for healing of the prostate, ovaries, and uterus.

00:43:11.880 --> 00:43:19.217
No more miscarriages.

00:43:19.640 --> 00:43:27.240
We call the wayward children home.

00:43:38.646 --> 00:43:46.631
I curse breast cancer; go now in Jesus' name.

00:43:55.907 --> 00:44:04.672
I call for healing of throat cancers and gum disease.

00:44:04.672 --> 00:44:11.400
I command Celiac disease to be healed.

00:44:11.400 --> 00:44:24.828
I thank You for restoring marriages.

00:44:29.404 --> 00:44:43.615
We believe for financial breakthroughs and creative ideas.

00:45:00.959 --> 00:45:01.239
Thank You, Father.

00:45:01.239 --> 00:45:03.239
Amen.

00:45:03.239 --> 00:45:13.680
Please subscribe to our channel.

00:45:13.680 --> 00:45:28.668
We're going back to the basics—teaching prayer.

00:45:28.668 --> 00:45:47.395
Remember Billie Brim's conference is October 16th to 21st in Branson.

00:45:48.648 --> 00:45:54.595
It will be a blessing.

00:45:54.595 --> 00:46:01.966
God bless you all.

00:46:01.966 --> 00:46:05.733
Jesus loves you.
